snippet.title: DEAD OR ALIVE 6 - Combat and Features Trailer
snippet.description:
Fighters DEAD OR ALIVE 6 is arriving worldwide on March 1st 2019. Here is a quick view of the DOA6 Battle system, modes and many other features upon its release.. 

Physical and Digital Pre-orders are available now. To get more information on the pre-order bonuses and digital deluxe please go here: https://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/us/products.html

Steel Book case available from Gamestop (U.S.) and EB Games (Canada) when you pre order DOA6 while supplies last.

[official site] http://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/
[official twitter] https://twitter.com/DOATEC_OFFICIAL
[official facebook] https://facebook.com/deadoralivegame
[official twitch] https://twitch.tv/Deadoralivegame

#DEADORALIVE6 #DOA6 #March1st
